dataIdInfo.idPurp:
This dataset was extracted from the City of Cape Town Street Name Dataset for use in APG2015F and APG4007F courses at the Geomatics Division, APG, University of Cape Town.
The Land Parcel feature class consists out of the City of Cape Town's Cadastre Information (properties) as populated by the departments involved with the Property Value Chain. Attribute information includes the legal status of the property.
dataIdInfo.idAbs:
This dataset was extracted from the City of Cape Town Street Name Dataset for use in APG2015F and APG4007F courses at the Geomatics Division, APG, University of Cape Town. The data provided to the students contains errors deliberately introduced.

The Land Parcel feature class consists out of the City of Cape Town's Cadastre Information as populated by various departments.
